title: KMSAuto Easy 1.06.V6 (Activator For Windows 7,8,8.1 and Office 1
description:
KMSAuto Easy 1.06.V6 (Activator For Windows 7,8,8.1 and Office 10,13)





Info:




Program name: KMSAuto Easy
Program Version: 1.06.V6
Author: Ratiborus
Language: Russian, English
Treatment: not required



Working with the program:
Run KMSAuto Easy
1 - Activate Windows
2 - Activate Office
3 - Activate Windows and Office
V - be validated online M $
F - To go on forum.ru-board.com
R - Summary
I - Set KMS-Service
U-Delete KMS-Service
Q - Exit




System requirements:
Windows Vista, 7, Windows 8, 8.1, Server 2012, Server 2012 R2, Office 2010/2013 VL edition.




Description:
KMSAuto Easy - Automatic KMS-activator for the operating systems Windows Vista, 7, 8, 8.1, Server 2012, and Office 2010/2013 VL edition. Works without installation, activation performs without leaving incriminating traces in the system. Based on CCM Server from mikmk38. Microsoft. NET Framework is required.
